name: Dike
description: Dike 11 Coin has been produced by using Smart Contract on TRC-20 platform of Tron blockchain in October 2020. The development purpose of DIKE Token is make transaction easier with minute gas fees on blockchain. DIKE will perform as utility token in blockchain financial system. DIKE Token known as Dike 11 has initially 40 crore supply with 8 digit precision. 40 Crore Coin (DIKE) will be in market circulation where 10 crore Coin will be used by company for own blockchain development, promotion, technical team expansion.
